File handling block:
- defence from opening the directoty;
- not existing file;
- no arguments;

Input data:
- invalid atoi value;
- not a number or space;
- empty file;
- empty line in the start, middle or end;
- max value of the monitor dimension;
- no tabs as separator;
- y not more then 2.000; in orde to have all pixels on the monitor;
- equal quantity of '\n';

Colors parsing:
- len [3-8];
- first element is char '0';
- second element is char 'x';
- possible elements after [ 0 - 9 ] || [ A - F ];
- if color is not valid -> the default color will be settled;
